   "body" : "Use Guix to produce a fully -static-pie x86_64-linux-gnu bitcoind using GCC 12.1.0 and glibc 2.35. The binary is ~15mb stripped, and includes wallet/upnp/natpmp/zmq etc. This builds on #25484 and #25391.\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# file bitcoind\r\n\tELF 64-bit LSB pie executable, x86-64, version 1 (GNU/Linux), static-pie linked, for GNU/Linux 3.2.0, stripped\r\n\r\n# ldd bitcoind\r\n\tstatically linked\r\n\r\n# ls -la bitcoind\r\n\t14831792 bitcoind\r\n```\r\n\r\nUsing glibc for static builds, would be less of a leap compared to switching to musl libc (POC in #23203).\r\n\r\nSo far I've tested the binary, including `test_bitcoin`, on a few different systems:\r\n* Ubuntu 22.04 with glibc 2.35 (latest glibc release)\r\n* Ubuntu 18.04 with glibc 2.27\r\n* Ubuntu 16.04 with glibc 2.24\r\n* CentOS 7 with glibc 2.17 (which is lower than our current minimum required of 2.18)\r\n* CentOS 8 with glibc 2.28\r\n* Alpine 3.16 with musl libc 1.2.3 (latest musl libc release)\r\n* Alpine 3.12 with musl libc 1.1.24\r\n\r\nI've also performed a full sync to the current tip (height=744166), and had the node running for a few days:\r\n\r\n[`-static-pie`](https://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc/Link-Options.html)\r\n> Produce a static position independent executable on targets that support it.\r\nA static position independent executable is similar to a static executable,\r\nbut can be loaded at any address without a dynamic linker.\r\n\r\nGuix Builds (x86_64):\r\n```bash\r\n4b8e98368a60ff77b91bf03c9b46633e9d36a7cbf4ccaa66be40e04bc886e0f1  guix-build-da9f731fb6d8/output/dist-archive/bitcoin-da9f731fb6d8.tar.gz\r\nc974826ab9b50dc2134afc0f4ee32afce423cc44e5ffdda0ff950b6b5a06b753  guix-build-da9f731fb6d8/output/x86_64-linux-gnu/SHA256SUMS.part\r\n0ddfd1f082e54eed0a38dc04cbae9ae2d1c14e83f3eeaff08efe415caaf459a0  guix-build-da9f731fb6d8/output/x86_64-linux-gnu/bitcoin-da9f731fb6d8-x86_64-linux-gnu-debug.tar.gz\r\nd99f3f88b0490a7b431eed9cad4f6ce0b82ce2c89fd90e45eacd2274960a1937  guix-build-da9f731fb6d8/output/x86_64-linux-gnu/bitcoin-da9f731fb6d8-x86_64-linux-gnu.tar.gz\r\n```",
